children.name: Supporting-text
children.characters: I just learned about this adoption opportunity. The pet adoption organization is looking for help with improving their connection with communities. If we volunteer wed basically take their dogs on walks and talk to people in the neighborhood. The dogs will be wearing adopt me vests which would help us start the conversations. Heres the link to sign up, I would love to do this together.

children.name: Supporting-text
children.characters: I think Im going to finally adopt that scruffy dog :)
